To všetko kvôli jeho zmiznutej dcére.

195
00:20:44,017 --> 00:20:46,087
Ale...

196
00:20:46,717 --> 00:20:48,116
ja ho úplne chápem.

197
00:20:48,117 --> 00:20:50,757
Ak by sa to stalo mne...

198
00:20:51,247 --> 00:20:52,647
Bože môj.

199
00:20:53,387 --> 00:20:55,787
Myslím, že by som spravil
všetko, čo by som mohol.

200
00:20:56,247 --> 00:20:58,947
